# Code owners for Linked-out.
#
# Combined with branch protection (require review from Code Owners), this means:
#   • a PR from anyone other than the owner needs @Kkartik14's approval to merge;
#   • the owner's own PRs merge without approval (admin bypass — GitHub never lets an
#     author approve their own PR);
#   • any change under a test/CI path below always routes review to @Kkartik14.
#
# The LAST matching pattern for a given file wins.

# Default owner for the whole repository.
*                           @Kkartik14

# ── Tests & test harnesses — changes here always require the owner's review. ────
/apps/api/test/             @Kkartik14
/apps/web/e2e/              @Kkartik14
**/*.test.ts                @Kkartik14
**/*.test.tsx               @Kkartik14
**/*.test.cjs               @Kkartik14
**/*.spec.ts                @Kkartik14

# ── CI & repo automation. ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                   @Kkartik14
/scripts/                   @Kkartik14
